<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="jumbotron">
            <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Stream Precision™</h1>
            <p class="lead"><p>This project was made by <strong>Tomáš Rohovský</strong> from class <strong>AIK2</strong>.</p>
            <hr class="my-4">
            <div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
                <p style="text-align: justify;">Welcome to the future of river stream measurement! Our company is at the forefront of this exciting field, providing the <strong>most accurate data on Earth</strong> through our <strong>state-of-the-art gauging stations</strong>. Our gauging stations are not just tools, they are the <strong>epitome of precision and reliability</strong>. They are designed to measure river streams with an <strong>accuracy that is unparalleled in the industry</strong>. This level of precision allows us to provide data that is not only reliable but also actionable, enabling our clients to make informed decisions based on the <strong>most accurate information available</strong>.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/List" role="button">Gauging Stations</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 text-right">
                    <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" href="/Home/About" role="button">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="/Images/img1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="img1">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/Images/img2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="img2">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/Images/img3.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="img3">
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="jumbotron mt-5">
            <div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
                <h2 class="my-4" style="text-align: justify;">Still Not Convinced about Gauging Stations?</h2>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">Are you hesitant about the effectiveness of traditional river stream measurement methods? It's time to reconsider with our state-of-the-art gauging stations that are revolutionizing the industry.</p>

                <h2 class="my-4" style="text-align: justify;">Unmatched Accuracy and Reliability</h2>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">Our gauging stations aren't just tools; they're the pinnacle of precision and reliability. With cutting-edge technology, they provide unparalleled accuracy in measuring river streams, ensuring the data you receive is dependable and actionable.</p>

                <h2 class="my-4" style="text-align: justify;">Embracing Advanced Technology</h2>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">Say goodbye to outdated methods and welcome the future with our gauging stations equipped with the latest technology. From advanced sensors to sophisticated data processing algorithms, we capture every detail of the river's flow, delivering high-resolution data unmatched by traditional methods.</p>

                <h2 class="my-4" style="text-align: justify;">Contributing to Global Understanding</h2>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">Beyond industry impact, our gauging stations play a crucial role in global efforts to understand and address climate change. By providing accurate data on river streams, we contribute to vital research and policymaking aimed at safeguarding our water resources for future generations.</p>

                <p class="mb-4" style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Ready to explore the future of river stream measurement? Join us on this transformative journey today!</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div style="height: 40px;"></div>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
